q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Every moment, our brains receive information from our senses and) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (decide how to respond. For children with Sensory Processing Disorder) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (\(SPD\) or autism, this system works differently.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (WHAT IS SENSORY PROCESSING?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (The brain's ability to receive, organize, and respond to sensory input.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (When this system is not working well, children may be:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (SENSORY SEEKING \(Hypo-sensitive / Under-responsive\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (- Craves intense input \(spinning, crashing, loud noises\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (- Seems to never get enough stimulation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (- May appear hyperactive or 'wild') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (- Has high pain tolerance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (SENSORY AVOIDING \(Hyper-sensitive / Over-responsive\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (- Overwhelmed by sounds, textures, lights, or movements) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (- May cover ears, refuse certain foods, avoid touch) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (- Can seem anxious, rigid, or have frequent meltdowns) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (- Has low pain tolerance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (MIXED PATTERN:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (- Many children are seekers in SOME areas and avoiders in others) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (- The same child may crave deep pressure but hate light touch) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (KEY PRINCIPLE: Behavior is COMMUNICATION.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (When a child is 'misbehaving,' they may be telling you their sensory) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td (needs are not being met. This workbook helps you understand and meet) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (those needs proactively.) Tj ET

